Text: Video color is screwed up, Video is pixelated. Can't believe somebody actually uploaded this video. Nearly a gig and a half of pure shit. Don't waste your time or bandwidth.

Yeah, not the greatest quality... but not *that* bad and still very watchable. These were lower resolution mp4's I picked up from somewhere.

It's a great documentary. Very much worth downloading and watching if you're interested in Lewis and Clark.
